<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>

<div class="pt-lg-5 pe-lg-5">
<script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<span property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem"><a aria-current="page" class="home" href="https://carnegieclassifications.acenet.edu" property="item" title="Go to CARNEGIE CLASSIFICATION OF INSTITUTIONS OF HIGHER EDUCATION." typeof="WebPage"><span property="name">Home</span></a><meta content="1" property="position"/></span></div>
<h1 class="entry-title">Institution Search</h1>
</div>
<div class="d-none d-md-block background-white rounded-circle p-4">
<img alt="Eyeglass Image" src="https://carnegieclassifications.acenet.edu/wp-content/themes/ace-carnegie-classifications/img/icon-search.svg" width="100%"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="carnegie-subnav container">
<ul class="nav">
<li class="current-menu-item nav-item"><a aria-current="page" class="nav-link" href="/institutions/" title="Institutions List">Institutions List</a></li>

</ul>

<div class="institute">
<div class="pt-3 p-lg-5 institute-filter">
<div>
<form action="/institutions" id="institute-filter-form">
<div>
<label class="form-label" for="inst" id="inst">SEARCH BY INSTITUTION NAME</label>
<div class="input-group mb-3">
<input aria-describedby="basic-addon3" class="form-control" id="inst" name="inst" type="text" value="csu fresno"/>
<button class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon3" onclick="submitTheForm()"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
</button>

<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>
<div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="search-filter-accordion">
<div class="accordion-item">
<h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
<button aria-controls="flush-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" class="accordion-button collapsed" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne" data-bs-toggle="collapse" type="button">
                                    CLASSIFICATIONS
                                </button>
</h2>
<div aria-labelledby="flush-headingOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample" id="flush-collapseOne">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p class="institution-classification-type-label"><a aria-controls="ic2025-filter" aria-expanded="false" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#ic2025-filter" role="button">Institutional Classification</a></p><ul class="institution-filter ic2025-filter collapse" id="ic2025-filter"><li class="institution-filter-subtitle"><a aria-controls="ic2025__associate-filter" aria-expanded="false" class="institute-filter-internal-collapse" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#ic2025__associate-filter" role="button">Associate</a></li><ul class="collapse" id="ic2025__associate-filter"><li class="institution-filter-item"><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="ic20251" name="ic2025[]" type="checkbox" value="1"/><label class="form-check-label" for="ic20251">Mixed Associate Large</label></div></li><li class="institution-filter-item"><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="ic20252" name="ic2025[]" type="checkbox" value="2"/><label class="form-check-label" for="ic20252">Mixed Associate Medium</label></div></li><li class="institution-filter-item"><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="ic20253" name="ic2025[]" type="checkbox" value="3"/><label class="form-check-label" for="ic20253">Mixed Associate Small</label></div></li><li class="institution-filter-item"><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="ic202511" name="ic2025[]" type="checkbox" value="11"/><label class="form-check-label" for="ic202511">Professions-focused Associate Large/Medium</label></div></li><li class="institution-filter-item"><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="ic202512" name="ic2025[]" type="checkbox" value="12"/><label class="form-check-label" for="ic202512">Professions-focused Associate Small</label></div></li></ul><li class="institution-filter-subtitle"><a aria-controls="ic2025__associatebaccalaureate-filter" aria-expanded="false" class="institute-filter-internal-collapse" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#ic2025__associatebaccalaureate-filter" role="button">Associate/Baccalaureate</a></li><ul class="collapse" id="ic2025__associatebaccalaureate-filter"><li class="institution-filter-item"><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="ic20254" name="ic2025[]" type="checkbox" value="4"/><label class="form-check-label" for="ic20254">Mixed Associate/Baccalaureate</label></div></li><li class="institution-filter-item"><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="ic202513" name="ic2025[]" type="checkbox" value="13"/><label class="form-check-label" for="ic202513">Professions-focused Associate/Baccalaureate</label></div></li></ul><li class="institution-filter-subtitle"><a <script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>

<script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>
</div>

<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>

<script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>

<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>

<script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>
</div>

<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>

<div class="pt-lg-5 pe-lg-5">
<script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>
</div>
</div>

<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>

<script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>
</div>

<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>

<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>

<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>

<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>

<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>
</div>
<h2>FILTERS</h2>
<a alt="Clear the filters" href="/institutions/" id="clearFiltersElem">Clear Filters</a>
<script>
                            function submitTheForm() {
                                document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form').submit();
                            }

                            function clearFilters(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                var formElement = document.getElementById('institute-filter-form');
                                formElement.reset();
                                var checkboxElems = document.querySelectorAll('.form-check-input');
                                for (var i = 0; i < checkboxElems.length; i++) {
                                    var checkboxElem = checkboxElems[i];
                                    checkboxElem.checked = false;
                                }
                            }
                        </script>

<script>
            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked
                var btnElem = document.querySelector('.show-' + type + '-archive-institution');
                console.log(btnElem);
                // .card-list-archive-institution or .table-archive-institution
                var cardListElem = document.querySelector('.card-list-archive-institution');
                var tableElem = document.querySelector('.table-archive-institution');

                // give other buttons under .institution-search-view-toggle the class of btn-light
                var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.institution-search-view-toggle .btn');
                for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                    var btn = btns[i];
                    btn.classList.remove('btn-light');
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    if (btn !== btnElem) {
                        btn.classList.add('btn-light');
                    } else {
                        btn.classList.add('active');
                    }
                }

                // toggle the display of the card list and table
                if (type === 'card-list') {
                    cardListElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    cardListElem.classList.add('d-none');
                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');
                }

                // save the selection in a cookie
                document.cookie = "archive_institution_view=" + type + "; path=/";
            }
        </script>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
<h3 class="text-blue-dark mb-0">
                0 Results            </h3>
<div class="d-flex gap-3">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    Download Results:
                    <a alt="Download CSV file" class="dataDownloadElem csvDownloadElem" href="#">CSV</a> |
                    <a alt="Download UID file" class="dataDownloadElem uidDownloadElem" href="#">UID</a>
</div>
<div aria-label="View Options" class="btn-group institution-search-view-toggle" role="group">
<button class="btn active show-table-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('table')" type="button">
<i aria-label="Table View" class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
</button>
<button class="btn btn-light show-card-list-archive-institution" onclick="toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay('card-list')" type="button">
<div class="card-piece"></div>
<div class="card-piece"></div>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-1 mb-3">
<div id="institutionFilterChips"></div>
</div>
<p>We did not find any institutions that match your search criteria.</p>
</div>

            function toggleInsitutionArchiveDisplay(type = 'table') {
                // get the button that was clicked

                    btn.classList.remove('active');

                    tableElem.classList.remove('d-none');

<script id="wpforms-user-journey-js" src="https://carnegieclassifications.acenet.edu/wp-content/plugins/wpforms-user-journey/assets/js/wpforms-user-journey.min.js?ver=1.5.0"></script>

<script>
        var accordions_active = null;
        var accordions_tabs_active = null;
    </script>
<script>
    (function() {
        /**
         * Code to support the CSV & UID downloads.
         */
        const searchDescription = getSearchDescription();

        let csvDownloadElems = document.getElementsByClassName("csvDownloadElem");
        let uidDownloadElems = document.getElementsByClassName("uidDownloadElem");

        initDownloadElements(csvDownloadElems, 'csv');
        initDownloadElements(uidDownloadElems, 'uid');

        /**
         * Initialize the download elements. THis should be a collection of anchors
         * used for the UID and CSV downloads. We're using this paradigm since there 
         * are currently duplicate download elements on the page.
         */
        function initDownloadElements(downloadCollection, intent) {
            for (let i = 0; i < downloadCollection.length; i++) {
                let elem = downloadCollection[i];
                // Add a data attribute called intent to the collection item (collection[i]) 
                // to be used when intent needs to be recalled.
                elem.setAttribute('data-intent', intent);

                // Homogenize the download elements.
                enableDownload(elem);

                elem.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    disableDownloadElements(downloadCollection);
                    resultDownload(intent, searchDescription).then(() => {
                        enableDownloadElements(downloadCollection);
                    });
                }, false);
            }
        }

        /**
         * Enable and initialize the download elements.
         */
        function enableDownloadElements(downloadCollection) {
            for (let i = 0; i < downloadCollection.length; i++) {
                let elem = downloadCollection[i];
                enableDownload(elem);
            }
        }

        /**
         * Disable the download elements.
         */
        function disableDownloadElements(downloadCollection) {
            for (let i = 0; i < downloadCollection.length; i++) {
                let elem = downloadCollection[i];
                disableDownload(elem);
            }
        }

        /**
         * Used when the button/anchor is clicked, this updates the UI
         * to indicate a download is in progress. It also disables the
         * download button so that users can't trigger multiple concurrent
         * file downloads.
         */
        function disableDownload(elem) {
            // Disable the element (anchor).
            elem.classList.add('disabled');
            elem.style.pointerEvents = 'none';
            elem.style.cursor = 'default';

            // Update element style to show spinner.
            elem.setAttribute('title', 'Downloading data...');
            enableSpinner(elem);
        }


        /**
         * Enable and initialize the download element.
         */
        function enableDownload(elem) {
            // Enable the element (anchor).
            elem.classList.remove('disabled');
            elem.style.pointerEvents = 'auto';
            elem.style.cursor = 'pointer';

            // Update element style to remove/hide spinner.
            let intent = elem.getAttribute('data-intent') || '';
            elem.setAttribute('title', 'Click to download ' + intent + ' data.');
            disableSpinner(elem);
        }

        /**
         * Used to show a spinner when the download is in progress.
         */
        function enableSpinner(elem) {
            elem.innerHTML = '<div class="spinner spinner-grow spinner-grow-sm mx-1" role="status"><span class="px-1 sr-only">Loading...</span></div></a>';
        }

        /**
         * Revert the anchor content and remove spinner.
         */
        function disableSpinner(elem) {
            let intent = elem.getAttribute('data-intent') || '';
            elem.innerHTML = intent.toUpperCase();
        }

        function getInputDescription(inputElement) {
            if (!inputElement) return '';

            var labelElem = document.querySelector('label[for="' + inputElement.id + '"]');
            var label = labelElem ? labelElem.textContent : '';
            var name = inputElement.getAttribute('name');
            var split = name ? name.split('__') : null;

            // Extra work is required if this has a parent.
            if (split && split.length > 1) {
                var parentItemId = split.join('').replace('[]', '');
                var parentElem = document.querySelector('input#' + parentItemId);
                var parentDescription = getInputDescription(parentElem)
                label = (parentDescription ? parentDescription : ' ' + parentItemId) + ": " + label;
            }

            return label;
        }

        function getSearchDescription() {
            var description = '';

            var nameElem = document.querySelector('input#inst');
            var nameVal = nameElem ? nameElem.value : '';
            if (nameVal) {
                description = "Name contains " + "'" + nameVal + "'";
            }

            var inputs = {};
            inputs['basic2021'] = 'Basic';
            inputs['ipug2021'] = 'Undergraduate Instructional Program';
            inputs['ipgrad2021'] = 'Graduate Instructional Program';
            inputs['enrprofile2021'] = 'Enrollment Profile';
            inputs['ugprofile2021'] = 'Undergraduate Profile';
            inputs['sizeset2021'] = 'Size and Setting';
            inputs['cce2020'] = 'Community Engagement';
            inputs['lpp'] = 'Leadership for Public Purpose';
            inputs['control'] = 'Control';
            inputs['iclevel'] = 'Level';
            inputs['stabbr'] = 'State';
            inputs['urbanization'] = 'Urbanicity';
            inputs['obereg'] = 'Region';

            Object.keys(inputs).forEach((key) => {
                var label = inputs[key];
                var form = document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form');
                var formElems = form.elements;
                var inputsArr = Array.from(formElems);
                var describe = '';
                inputsArr.forEach((item) => {
                    // All our inputs are checkboxes except institution name (inst).
                    if (item.checked && item.id.startsWith(key)) {
                        var label = getInputDescription(item);
                        describe += (describe.length ? ' or ' : '') + "'" + label + "'";
                    }
                });

                description += (description && description.length && describe && describe.length ? ' and ' :
                    '');
                description += (describe && describe.length ? label + ' = ' : '')
                description += (describe && describe.length ? describe : '');
            });

            var inputs = {};
            // These need to be handled differently.
            inputs['womens'] = 'Women\'s Colleges';
            inputs['hbcu'] = 'Historically Black Colleges and Universities';
            inputs['hsi'] = 'Hispanic Serving Institutions';
            inputs['tribal'] = 'Tribal Colleges';
            inputs['msi'] = 'Minority Serving Institutions';
            inputs['landgrnt'] = 'Land Grant';
            // inputs['coplac'] = 'Council of Public Liberal Arts Colleges';
            // inputs['cusu'] = 'Coalition of Urban Serving or Urban & Metropolitan Universities (CUSU/CUMU)';

            Object.keys(inputs).forEach((key) => {
                var label = inputs[key];
                var form = document.querySelector('#institute-filter-form');
                var formElems = form.elements;
                var inputsArr = Array.from(formElems);
                var describe = '';
                inputsArr.forEach((item) => {
                    // All our inputs are checkboxes except institution name (inst).
                    if (item.checked && item.id.startsWith(key)) {
                        var label = getInputDescription(item);
                        describe += (describe.length ? ' or ' : '') + "'" + label + "'";
                    }
                });

                description += (description && description.length && describe && describe.length ? ' and ' :
                    '');
                description += (describe && describe.length ? label + ' = ' : '')
                description += (describe && describe.length ? 'Yes' : '');
            });

            return description;
        }

        function resultDownload(format, description = "This is a client-side description to be generated dynamically.") {
            return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                var fileType = format && format.toLowerCase().trim() === 'uid' ? 'uid' : 'csv';
                var url = new URL(window.location.href);

                url.searchParams.append('format', fileType);
                url.searchParams.append('descr', description);

                fetch(url)
                    .then(response => {
                        if (!response.ok) {
                            throw new Error('Network response was not ok');
                        }
                        return response.blob();
                    })
                    .then(blob => {
                        const a = document.createElement('a');
                        const objectURL = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
                        a.href = objectURL;
                        a.target = "_blank";
                        a.download = 'ace-institutional-classifications.' + fileType;
                        document.body.appendChild(a);
                        a.click();

                        // Clean up the object URL and remove the anchor element
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            URL.revokeObjectURL(objectURL);
                            document.body.removeChild(a);
                            resolve(); // Resolve the promise when the download is initiated
                        }, 1000); // Adjust the delay as needed (1000ms = 1 second)
                    })
                    .catch(error => {
                        console.error('Error fetching the file:', error);
                        reject(error); // Reject the promise if an error occurs
                    });
            });
        }

        function getPillDescription(theFilter) {
            let theLabelElem = document.querySelector('label[for="' + theFilter.id + '"]');
            let theLabel = theLabelElem.textContent;

            var name = theFilter.name.split('[]')[0];
            var segments = name.split('__');
            var segment = segments.pop();
            var parentName = segments.join('__') + '[]';
            var nextUps = document.querySelectorAll('input[name="' + parentName + '"]');
            var nextUp = null;

            for (const next of nextUps) {
                if (next.value == segment) {
                    nextUp = next;
                }
            }

            if (nextUp) {
                return getPillDescription(nextUp) + ": " + theLabel
            }

            var ocElem = document.querySelector('a[aria-controls="' + segment + '-filter' + '"]');

            if (ocElem) {
                theLabel = ocElem.textContent + ': ' + theLabel;
            }

            return theLabel;
        }

        /**
         * Fill out pills based on selected checkboxes
         */
        function updateFilterPills() {
            let checkedFilters = document.querySelectorAll("#institute-filter-form input:checked");
            let pillBox = document.getElementById("institutionFilterChips");
            let allFilters = [];
            for (i = 0; i < checkedFilters.length; i++) {
                let theFilter = checkedFilters[i];
                let theId = theFilter.id;
                // let theText = theFilter.parentElement.textContent;
                let theText = getPillDescription(theFilter);

                dataLayer.push({
                    'event': 'carnegieSearchFilterItem',
                    'value': theText,
                });
                allFilters.push(theText);
                // create the pill element
                let button = document.createElement("button");

                button.classList.add(
                    "institution-filter-chip", "btn", "btn-outline-primary",
                    "gap-2", "btn-sm", "d-flex-inline", "align-items-center", "px-3", "me-3", "mb-3"
                );

                button.setAttribute('data-filter-id', theId);

                button.append(theText);
                let icon = document.createElement("i");
                icon.classList.add("fa-solid", "fa-x", "fa-xs", "ms-2");
                button.append(icon);
                pillBox.append(button);
            }
            if (allFilters.length > 0) {
                dataLayer.push({
                    'event': 'carnegieSearchFilter',
                    'value': allFilters.join("|")
                });
            }
            attachChipEvents();
        }

        // remove a chip and the associated checkmark and submit the filter form
        function removeChipFilter(chipEle) {
            let id = chipEle.dataset.filterId;
            document.getElementById(id).checked = false;
            chipEle.remove();
            document.getElementById("institute-filter-form").submit();
        }

        // attach the click event to remove checkbox check when removing chip
        function attachChipEvents() {
            const chipElems = document.getElementsByClassName("institution-filter-chip");

            for (var i = 0; i < chipElems.length; i++) {
                chipElems[i].addEventListener('click', (event) => {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    // This allows us to get the button whether the button or the icon were clicked.
                    var target = event.target.tagName.toLowerCase() === 'button' ? event.target : event.target
                        .parentNode;
                    removeChipFilter(target);
                }, false);
            }
        }

        updateFilterPills();
    })();
</script>
<style>
    .institute a.dataDownloadElem {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 2em;
        max-width: 2em;
        min-width: 2em;
        overflow: hidden;
        vertical-align: bottom;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>
